# Advanced Topics in Software Systems Design and Implementation HW1

## PART 1 - Add new system call to Linux
* add new system call number at linux/include/uapi/asm-generic/unistd.h
* implement the function at linux/kernel/sys.c
* The kernel patch is named "patch" in the same directory
 
## PART 2 - Write a simple shell in C
* support cd, exit, getcpu, execution

